<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-8 px-4">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Paired Mode</h1>
  
  <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <p class="mb-4">Paired mode connects you with another FlowGrind user for mutual accountability.</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">How Paired Mode Works:</h2>
    
    <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 mb-4">
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Join the Queue</strong>
        <p>Enter the matchmaking system to find an accountability partner</p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Set Mutual Goals</strong>
        <p>Share your session goals with your partner</p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Stake Credits</strong>
        <p>Both users stake credits for the session</p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Work Together</strong>
        <p>Focus for 25 minutes with optional video and chat</p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Progress Check-ins</strong>
        <p>Brief check-ins to share progress during the session</p>
      </li>
      
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Mutual Validation</strong>
        <p>At the end, validate each other's work</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
    
    <p class="bg-blue-100 p-3 rounded">
      <strong>Benefit:</strong> Paired sessions have higher success rates as mutual accountability keeps you focused!
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="flex justify-between">
      <%= link_to "← Back", onboarding_solo_mode_path, class: "bg-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-400 text-gray-800 font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded" %>
      <%= link_to "Next: Validation", onboarding_validation_path, class: "bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>